_start":44.17,"time_end":47.58},{"position":17,"content":"I'd like more information about public transport.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/17.mp3","time_start":47.58,"time_end":50.66},{"position":18,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/18.mp3","time_start":50.66,"time_end":51.91},{"position":19,"content":"In that case the quickest and most comfortable is a cab","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/19.mp3","time_start":52.4,"time_end":56.39},{"position":20,"content":"and of course there are always plenty available.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/20.mp3","time_start":56.39,"time_end":58.8},{"position":21,"content":"But it'll cost you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/21.mp3","time_start":58.8,"time_end":60.1},{"position":22,"content":"You can also take a Greyhound bus or there's an Airport Shuttle Service to Milton.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/22.mp3","time_start":60.27,"time_end":65.31},{"position":23,"content":"Uh, I think for that kind of distance a cab would be way beyond my budget.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/23.mp3","time_start":65.93,"time_end":70.15},{"position":24,"content":"But the bus sounds OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/24.mp3","time_start":70.15,"time_end":72.26},{"position":25,"content":"Can you tell me how much that would cost?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/