dress.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/43.mp3","time_start":121.27,"time_end":127.6},{"position":44,"content":"It's a door-to-door service and it would suit you much better, because there's one every two hours.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/44.mp3","time_start":128.07,"time_end":132.98},{"position":45,"content":"So how much does that cost?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/45.mp3","time_start":132.98,"time_end":134.59},{"position":46,"content":"Let's see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/46.mp3","time_start":134.8,"time_end":136.03},{"position":47,"content":"Yeah, that's $35 one way, $65 return,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/47.mp3","time_start":137.19,"time_end":141.7},{"position":48,"content":"so I guess it's a bit more expensive than the Greyhound.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/48.mp3","time_start":141.7,"time_end":144.77},{"position":49,"content":"Oh, that doesn't sound too bad,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/49.mp3","time_start":144.77,"time_end":146.79},{"position":50,"content":"especially if it'll take me straight to the hotel.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/50.mp3","time_start":146.79,"time_end":149.65},{"position":51,"content":"But you do need to reserve a seat.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/51.mp3","time_sta