0-53-48/60.mp3","time_start":173.05,"time_end":176.97},{"position":61,"content":"And this is for just one person or...?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/61.mp3","time_start":176.97,"time_end":180.03},{"position":62,"content":"Yeah, just me, please.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/62.mp3","time_start":180.57,"time_end":181.99},{"position":63,"content":"Right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/63.mp3","time_start":181.99,"time_end":182.71},{"position":64,"content":"And you said your expected time of arrival was 11.30?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/64.mp3","time_start":182.71,"time_end":186.61},{"position":65,"content":"So if I book your Shuttle for after 12.00 - let's say 12.30,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/65.mp3","time_start":186.61,"time_end":191.71},{"position":66,"content":"that should give you plenty of time to, you know, collect your baggage, maybe grab a coffee?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/66.mp3","time_start":191.71,"time_end":196.7},{"position":67,"content":"Yeah, that sounds fine, as long as we land on time!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/67.mp3","time_start":196.7,"time_end":200.29},{"position":68,"content":"Well, we'll take your flight details so you don't need to worry too much about that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/68.mp3","time_start":200.29,"time_end":205.02},{"position":69,"content":"Now, what about the fare?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/69.mp3","time_start":205.02,"time_end":207.49},{"position":70,"content":"What sort of ticket do you want?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/70.mp3","time_start":207.49,"time_end":208.98},{"position":71,"content":"One way or...?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/71.mp3","time_start":208.98,"time_end":210.14},{"position":72,"content":"Yeah, that'll be fine, provided I can book the return trip once I'm there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/72.mp3","time_start":210.14,"time_end":214.79},{"position":73,"content":"No problem - just allow a couple of days in advance to make sure you get a seat.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/73.mp3","time_start":214.79,"time_end":219.38},{"position":74,"content":"And what is your name, please?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/74.mp3","time_start":219.81,"time_end":221.69},{"position":75,"content":"Janet, Janet Thomson.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/75.mp3","time_start":221.69,"time_end":224.05},{"position":76,"content":"Is that Thompson spelt with a 'p'?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/76.mp3","time_start":224.05,"time_end":226.47},{"position":77,"content":"No, it's THOMSON.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/77.mp3","time_start":226.47,"time_end":230.81},{"position":78,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/78.mp3","time_start":231.03,"time_end":232.11},{"position":79,"content":"And you'll be coming from the UK?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/79.mp3","time_start":232.11,"time_end":234.56},{"position":80,"content":"What flight will you be traveling on?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/80.mp3","time_start":234.56,"time_end":236.56},{"position":81,"content":"Oh, it's Air Canada flight number AC936, from London Heathrow.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/81.mp3","time_start":236.56,"time_end":243.52},{"position":82,"content":"Right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/82.mp3","time_start":243.52,"time_end":245.01},{"position":83,"content":"Now, do you know where you'll be staying?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/83.mp3","time_start":245.21,"time_end":247.63},{"position":84,"content":"We need to give the driver an address.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/84.mp3","time_start":247.63,"time_end":249.57},{"position":85,"content":"Yes, it's called the Vacation Motel","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/85.mp3","time_start":249.57,"time_end":252.75},{"position":86,"content":"and I think it's near the town centre.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/86.mp3","time_start":252.75,"time_end":255.27},{"position":87,"content":"Anyway, the address is 24, Kitchener Street -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/87.mp3","time_start":255.27,"time_end":259.29},{"position":88,"content":"that's KITCHENER Street.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/88.mp3","time_start":259.29,"time_end":265.39},{"position":89,"content":"That's fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/89.mp3","time_start":265.93,"time_end":267.18},{"position":90,"content":"Right, so that's $35 to pay, please. Have you got your credit card number there?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/90.mp3","time_start":267.51,"time_end":272.88},{"position":91,"content":"Yes, it's a VISA card,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/91.mp3","time_start":272.88,"time_end":275.51},{"position":92,"content":"and the number is 3303 8450 2045 6837.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/92.mp3","time_start":275.51,"time_end":286.31},{"position":93,"content":"OK. Well, that seems to be everything.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/93.mp3","time_start":286.43,"time_end":289.1},{"position":94,"content":"Have a good trip and we'll see you in Toronto next week!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-1-part-1-2023-07-28-10-53-48/94.mp3","time_start":289.1,"time_end":292.31},{"position":95,"content":"Yes, bye. Oh, thanks for your help!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test